%h2 The 24 BipolarTypes
%p The MBTI only has 16 types, because they assume that Physical & Mental and Affective & Financial are opposites. BipolarType does not group the four Realms into two sets of two so there are 24 BipolarTypes (4x3x2 instead of 4x2x2)
